What you need to know:

It is obvious that the best way to save a victim of SGBV is to remove them from the dangerous fangs and chokehold of the perpetrator to safety.To its credit, Makueni County government is the only devolved unit so far to establish an alternative and safe accommodation to shelter SGBC survivors.During the Covid-19 offensive, the privately run shelters have played a major and critical role in offering life-saving services.